                {
                    "name": "Chupar",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Requirements </b>The chupacabra has a creature <a aonid=\"20\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">grabbed</a>; <b>Effect </b>The chupacabra sucks blood from the grabbed creature. The chupacabra gains the <a aonid=\"32\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">quickened</a> condition for 1 minute and can use the extra action only for Strike and Stride actions. A chupacabra can't use Chupar again while it is quickened in this way. A creature that has its blood drained by a chupacabra is <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">drained 1</a> until it receives healing (of any kind or amount).",
